 noticed the bot had stopped, he slowed&lt;br&gt; down and stopped some distance from the target, not wanting to engage&lt;br&gt; by himself.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &quot;We wont let you go back into the city and attack innocent civilians,&quot;&lt;br&gt; Perseus shouted.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; As Ravenchief came up behind Perseus, there was a massive shockwave&lt;br&gt; that shot through the structure of the tunnel, as the shockwave hit,&lt;br&gt; the power shorted out and the remaining forcefields shut off along&lt;br&gt; with the power to the rest of the city.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; Trelos sat in bewilderment he struggled to comprehend what was going&lt;br&gt; on, but shortly came to and charged down the hallway toward the exit.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &quot;After him!&quot; shouted Perseus and he resumed his pursuit.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; On 8/18/07, CatMaster o &lt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:CatMastero%40yahoo.com&quot;&gt;CatMastero@yahoo.&lt;wbr&gt;com&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt; &gt; &quot;I&#39;ve reached the patient.  I&#39;ll begin treatment imminently.&quot; Kenzo&lt;br&gt; &gt; announced as he began assessing the guard&#39;s condition.&lt;br&gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt;
 &gt; --- In &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:nbwrpg%40yahoogroups.com&quot;&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.&lt;wbr&gt;com&lt;/a&gt;, Kraftlos &lt;kraftlos@..&lt;wbr&gt;.&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Be my guest!&quot; shouted Perseus into his radio as he struggled to&lt;br&gt; &gt; keep up&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; with the fleeing prisoner.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; As they reached a spot about 3/4 of the way down the tunnel, Trelos&lt;br&gt; &gt; suddenly&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; discovered that the forcefields were powered and on.  (this section&lt;br&gt; &gt; was&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; actually running off the city&#39;s power grid and not the base&#39;s).&lt;br&gt; &gt; Trelos ran&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; full-force into the forcefield and was thrown backward violently&lt;br&gt; &gt; causing him&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; to yelp in surprise and perhaps pain.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; Meanwhile...&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &quot;Forget about the armory, I think our culprit got out the other&lt;br&gt; &gt; way!&quot;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; shouted Salveo to the troopers as he walked down to the area where&lt;br&gt; &gt;
 Rodimus&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; and Dinobot were.  &quot;Where&#39;s Kenzo?  We have a guard down, I hope&lt;br&gt; &gt; its not too&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; late to save him.&quot;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; Ravenchief was far more interested in getting this prisoner.  He had&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; received severe damage in their last encounter and he had no&lt;br&gt; &gt; intention of&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; letting this bot go freely in the city again.  He ran down the&lt;br&gt; &gt; stairs,&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; glanced at the smashed up prison area, then took off down the&lt;br&gt; &gt; passageway to&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; help Lord Perseus.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; On 8/15/07, Nic &lt;warriorazure@&lt;wbr&gt;...&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;   Dinobot had ignored the earlier snickering. He transformed to&lt;br&gt; &gt; raptor&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; mode and followed Kup and Rodimus as they tracked Trelos.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Dinobot: That prisoner looks... viral. It&#39;s as if there&#39;s a&lt;br&gt; &gt; glitch in&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
 his processors. His reasoning patterns seem illogical from the&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; decisions he made... If you two want, I can attack him in close&lt;br&gt; &gt; combat.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:nbwrpg%40yahoogroups.com&quot;&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.&lt;wbr&gt;com&lt;/a&gt; &lt;nbwrpg%40yahoogrou&lt;wbr&gt;ps.com&gt;, Richard&lt;br&gt; &gt; Allen&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &lt;roborick007@&lt;wbr&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; ::Rodimus Prime/Kup::&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus and Kup follow Perseus dpwn the hall after the escaped&lt;br&gt; &gt; Predacon.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Kup: If I get a firing solution I&#39;m taking it.&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Kraftlos &lt;kraftlos@&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Salveo and the troopers rush to the first partition which&lt;br&gt; &gt; separated&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; the command center hallway from the more open entrance area. He&lt;br&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; walked up to the
